017 package com.crossideas.ap.common.external.enums;
018
019/**
020 * The Enum RequestResponse. <li>{@link #AUTHORIZED}</li>
021 * 
022 * <li>{@link #REJECTED}</li>
023 * 
024 * <li>{@link #WAITING_ASYNCHRONOUS}</li>
025 * 
026 * <li>{@link #WAITING_SYNCHRONOUS}</li>
027 * 
028 */
029public enum RequestResponse {
030
031        /** The authorized. */
032        AUTHORIZED(1, "AUTHORIZED"),
033
034        /** The rejected. */
035        REJECTED(2, "REJECTED"),
036
037        /** The waiting asynchronous. */
038        WAITING_ASYNCHRONOUS(3, "WAITING_ASYNCHRONOUS"),
039
040        /** The waiting synchronous. */
041        WAITING_SYNCHRONOUS(4, "WAITING_SYNCHRONOUS"), ;
042
043        /** The code. */
044        private int code;
045
046        /** The value. */
047        private String value;
048
049        /**
050         * Instantiates a new request response.
051         *
052         * @param code
053         *            the code
054         * @param value
055         *            the value
056         */
057        private RequestResponse(int code, String value) {
058                this.code = code;
059                this.value = value;
060        }
061
062        /**
063         * Gets the value.
064         *
065         * @return the value
066         */
067        public String getValue() {
068                return value;
069        }
070
071        /**
072         * Sets the value.
073         *
074         * @param value
075         *            the new value
076         */
077        public void setValue(String value) {
078                this.value = value;
079        }
080
081        /**
082         * Gets the code.
083         *
084         * @return the code
085         */
086        public int getCode() {
087                return code;
088        }
089
090        /**
091         * Sets the code.
092         *
093         * @param code
094         *            the new code
095         */
096        public void setCode(int code) {
097                this.code = code;
098        }
099
100        /**
101         * Gets the.
102         *
103         * @param code
104         *            the code
105         * @return the request response
106         */
107        public static RequestResponse get(int code) {
108
109                RequestResponse[] list = RequestResponse.values();
110                for (int i = 0; i < list.length; i++) {
111                        if (code == (list[i].getCode())) {
112                                return list[i];
113                        }
114                }
115                return null;
116        }
117}
